Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.45,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Hey what is it？Watch your step now！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.20,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}常識なんか要らない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:06.95,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.91,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}No No No don't worry 1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.08,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}吹き返す　心臓のリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:16.38,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}視界まだ眩んでる　それでも行かなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:23.51,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}キミが信じてる僕を裏切る わけにいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.64,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}強くクラクションが鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.31,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}孤独なまま時が経ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.69,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}逃げる事覚えたって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.98,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}新しい今日が来ちゃうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.36,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}この願い例え魔法が無くたって
